      <h1 class="display-1">How to Become a Mortgage Underwriter</h1>
      <p class="lead hero-subtitle">A mortgage underwriter is the decision-maker who evaluates risk and approves loans. It's a respected, analytical, in-demand role across lenders &mdash; and a strong way to build deep expertise in the mortgage business.</p>
